<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <title>Feature Disabled - Veritas</title>

    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <link rel="icon" href="/icon.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="icon" href="/icon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "tailwind", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag :app, "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>

    <style>
      body {
        background-image: url('<%= asset_path('frame.png') %>');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-attachment: fixed;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .gradient-overlay {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: -1;
      }

      .error-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 20px;
        position: relative;
      }

      .error-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 40px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #1f2937;
      }

      .error-icon {
        font-size: 4rem;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        opacity: 0.7;
      }

      .error-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #111827;
        text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      }

      .error-message {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        color: #374151;
        text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .error-details {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
      }

      .error-details h3 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: #111827;
      }

      .error-details p {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        color: #4b5563;
      }

      .glass-button {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4) !important;
        backdrop-filter: blur(5px) !important;
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(5px) !important;
        border: 2px solid rgba(82, 122, 154, 1) !important;
        color: #1f2937 !important;
        text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7) !important;
        transition: all 0.3s ease !important;
        position: relative !important;
        z-index: 10 !important;
        font-weight: 600 !important;
        text-decoration: none !important;
        display: inline-block !important;
        padding: 12px 24px !important;
        border-radius: 8px !important;
        margin: 8px !important;
      }

      .glass-button:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6) !important;
        border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5) !important;
        transform: translateY(-1px) !important;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) !important;
        color: #111827 !important;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="gradient-overlay"></div>

    <div class="error-container">
      <div class="error-card">
        <div class="error-icon">ðŸ”’</div>

        <h1 class="error-title">Feature Disabled</h1>

        <p class="error-message">
          The feature you're trying to access is currently disabled by a feature flag.
        </p>

        <div class="error-details">
          <h3>What does this mean?</h3>
          <p>This admin feature is controlled by a feature flag that hasn't been enabled for your account yet.</p>
          <p>Feature flags allow administrators to safely roll out new functionality or temporarily disable features for maintenance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="error-details">
          <h3>What can you do?</h3>
          <% if current_user&.superadmin? %>
            <p><strong>You're an admin!</strong> Check the Flipper admin panel to enable the required feature flag. Reach out to @jasper if you need help.</p>
            <%= link_to "â† Back to Home", root_path, class: "glass-button" %>
            <%= link_to "Flipper Admin", "/admin/flipper", class: "glass-button" %>
          <% elsif current_user&.admin? %>
            <p>Reach out to @jasper in slack.</p>
            <%= link_to "â† Back to Home", root_path, class: "glass-button" %>
          <% else %>
            <p>Contact <a href="mailto:support@phish.directory">support@phish.directory</a> to request access to this feature.</p>
            <%= link_to "â† Back to Home", root_path, class: "glass-button" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
